<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;6;9256" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB6,9256</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="1"/><gap extent="22" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 


    <lb n="2"/><gap extent="16" reason="lost" unit="character"/> ἔφη παραγε-

    <lb n="3"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νόμενον</supplied> Δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιόδ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ρον τὸν πρὸς τῆι <expan><ex cert="high">ἑκατοστῇ</ex></expan> <num value=" 1/100 "/> 

    <lb n="4"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῶν π</supplied>ερὶ Φιλ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>δελφείαν τόπων 

    <lb n="5"/>δοῦναι αὐτῶι εἰς τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">πεντηκοστὴν</ex></expan> <num value=" 1/50 "/> ἣν σὺ 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>ἐξειλήφῃς</corr><sic>εξειληφηις</sic></choice> χαλκοῦ <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντον</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> καὶ 

    <lb n="7"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γρ</supplied>άψαι τούτωι ἔχειν εἰς τὴν 

    <lb n="8"/>κ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>θήκουσαν ἀναφορὰν τοῦ <expan><ex cert="high">ταλάντου</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ οργιλως ἀπὸ τοῦ <subst><add place="inline">κτήματος</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">κτημ<gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> 

    <lb n="10"/>ὠρίζετο μὲν μήτ᾽ ἐντολὴν 

    <lb n="11"/>δεδωκέναι τοῖς περὶ τὸν 

    <lb n="12"/>Ἀπολλώνιον μήτε <choice><corr>δώσειν</corr><sic>δωσιν</sic></choice> ἕως 

    <lb n="13"/>τοῦ με παραγενέσθαι. σ᾽ οὖν 

    <lb n="14"/>καλῶς ποιήσεις ἐκ παντὸς 

    <lb n="15"/>τρόπου, ἐὰν δύνῃ παρα-

    <lb n="16"/>γενέσθαι, παραγενηθείς, 

    <lb n="17"/>ὅπως περὶ τούτων φροντίσω-

    <lb n="18"/>μεν. σοῦ γράψαντος φροντιεῖν ὅπως 

    <lb n="19"/>συναγοράσωμεν Ζήνωνι οἶνον 

    <lb n="20"/>παλαιοῦ Φιλαδελφείου οἴνου <expan>κε<ex cert="high">ράμια</ex></expan> <num value="9">θ</num> 

    <lb n="21"/>ὁμοίως οὗ ἀπέστειλας ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="22"/>πέρυσι <num value="6">ϛ</num> <num value="1/2">𐅵</num>, <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="35">λε</num> <num value="1/2">𐅵</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>διασάφησον δ᾽ ἡμῖν τίνες αἱ τιμαί εἰσιν καὶ πόσα <choice><corr>αἰτεῖς</corr><sic>ετις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="2"/>καὶ μὴ βράδυ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νε</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/>ἡμᾶς κινεῖν <choice><corr>ἐνταῦθα</corr><sic>ενταυτα</sic></choice>.  ἐπιμελοῦ δὲ καὶ σαυτοῦ ἵν᾽ <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνῃς.</corr><sic>υγιαινηις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4" rend="inverse"/>                            Ἑρμίαι </ab></div></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 190 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. den Zeitraum des Archivs; dazu BL VIII, S. 513. Gehört zum Leon - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Yale</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">6203</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0228</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0228;1;40" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">513</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">SB VI 9256</bibl></div><div n="meta.6203" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>